ok i give u an example. u have some info "A" u want to store. u show everyone what "A" is  then everyone puts it in an envelope & chops & seals it
now u have another info "B" u want to store. u take the "A" envelope  and "B"  and put this in a bigger envelope. then u show everyone  then seal the envelope  n everyone chops and signs it

now u have another info "C" u want to store. u take the "B" envelope (wich also has the "A" envelope)  and "C"  and put this in a bigger envelope. then u show everyone  then seal the envelope  n everyone chops and signs it
the envelopes are "blocks"  and everyone signing again and again is the "chain". that's it!
